Teorija:
Vienintelis objektas (angl. singleton)
Ensure a class has only one instance, and provide a global point of access to it.
Problem: application needs one, and only one, instance of an object. Additionally, lazy initialization and global access are necessary.

1 uzduotis:
Programa, kuri priims pranesimus (ClientOne, ClienTwo, MainForTest, ProgramLogger)
2 uzduotis:
Programa, kuri spausdina kolekcijas, kurias mes jam paduodame (PrintSpooler, TaskManager)

